<div class="landing-page">
  <div class="wrapper background-blue">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="container" style="padding-top:18vh;">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <h1 class="title">你与牛人之间只差这最后一课</h1>
            <h4 class="slogan">认知是人与人之前唯一的门槛，但人人都能通过掌握认知学习法完成认知升级</h4>
            <br/>
            <%= link_to products_path, class: "btn btn-danger btn-lg btn-round btn-raised" do %>
            <%= fa_icon("play", text: "开始上课") %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main main-raised">
      <div class="section text-center section-head">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
            <h2 class="title">不仅要「得到」，还要「做到」</h2>
            <h5 class="description">以认知科学原理为基础，我们打造了科学高效的认知学习法
              <br>帮助人们快速提升学习效率，完成认知升级
              <br>同时，我们以认知学习法重塑了职业技能教育
              <br>不仅要「得到」，还要让你快速从零到「做到」
              <br>
            </h5>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2" id="progresses">

              <div class="barWrapper">
                <span class="progressText">
                  <B>平面设计</B>
                </span>
                <div class="progress">
                  <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="85" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
                    <span class="popOver" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="85%"></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="barWrapper">
                <span class="progressText">
                  <B>营销策划</B>
                </span>
                <div class="progress ">
                  <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-info" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="75" aria-valuemin="10" aria-valuemax="100">
                    <span class="popOver" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="75%"></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="barWrapper">
                <span class="progressText">
                  <B>写作</B>
                </span>
                <div class="progress">
                  <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="71" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
                    <span class="popOver" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="71%"></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="barWrapper">
                <span class="progressText">
                  <B>摄影</B>
                </span>
                <div class="progress">
                  <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-warning" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="68" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
                    <span class="popOver" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="68%"></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="barWrapper">
                <span class="progressText">
                  <B>手绘</B>
                </span>
                <div class="progress">
                  <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-danger" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="70" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
                    <span class="popOver" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="70%"></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section section-content">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">

              <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1">
                <div class="section-description">
                  <h2 class="title">手把手极简教程</h2>
                  <h5 class="description">以「做到」为原则的教程体系，第一件事就是输出完整作品。步骤详细到无需思考，照做就行。
                  </h5>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-6 ">
                <div class="image-container">
                  <!-- 实在找不到类，样式写在表单里-->
                  <img style="width: 100%;" src="https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNbRwgy1fg02h3qy53j31b30z1wi9.jpg">
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-content">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">

              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="image-container">
                  <!-- 实在找不到类，样式写在表单里-->
                  <img style="width: 100%;" src="https://ws2.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNbRwgy1fg02glp0h3j310b0m5jvk.jpg">
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1">
                <div class="section-description">
                  <h2 class="title">学习游戏化</h2>
                  <h5 class="description">不同的课程内容，将被设计成不同的策略、竞技、对抗游戏，让大家通过游戏速成新技能。
                  </h5>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-content">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">

              <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1">
                <div class="section-description">
                  <h2 class="title">全程辅导</h2>
                  <h5 class="description">不定期邀请牛人分享，通过线下聚会、及线上社群进行社会化学习，老师全程答疑。
                  </h5>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="image-container">
                  <!-- 实在找不到类，样式写在表单里-->
                  <img style="width: 100%;" src="https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNbRwgy1fg02gidqsbj314010bn0k.jpg">
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container referrer">
          <div class="section text-center">
            <h2 class="title">牛人推荐</h2>

            <div class="team">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
